reviewText: The sound tracks on 4 of the 6 movies were horried.  Sounded hollow and scratchy all the way through--or at least as far as I could take watching them.  I was going to return the disks but was told to keep them at no charge.
The movies were just as described.  We enjoyed only one.  The others were not to our taste.  We're elderly and our tastes were shaped at an earlier time.
good movies. Its a good deal when you get 6 movies for the price of one. I like good deals.
Good Value, Good movies. I enjoyed them all. The convenience of having them in the same package and at a great price is very much appreciated. Thanks.

While I do not like to rate films as everyone has their own preferences....my main objection
is NOT the films but the packaging.
When you buy movies in a set there is danger of one (in my case) coming loose and it was
so badly scratched from wiggling around the spindle that it could not be used.
I gave the whole thing away after one film.

The movies arrived on time and in excellent shape. These are lighthearted stories just for being entertained. It is great to have all of them together and I am looking for other package deals of similar movies.
Good Value set to watch on a rainy night or a sick day when you are in bed!
These were a fun collection at an excellent price!
